WEBVTT

00:00:01.012 --> 00:00:05.229
Cybercrime is out of control.

00:00:06.186 --> 00:00:07.551
It's everywhere.

00:00:07.575 --> 00:00:11.863
We hear about it every single day.

00:00:12.771 --> 00:00:13.985
This year,

00:00:14.009 --> 00:00:19.143
over two billion records lost or stolen.

00:00:20.050 --> 00:00:25.685
And last year, 100 million of us,
mostly Americans,

00:00:25.709 --> 00:00:30.843
lost our health insurance data
to thieves -- myself included.